{"tid":869403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"做一半女喊停 他「快出來了hold不住」挨告","createTime":"2018-10-20T10:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T12:15:28.000Z","uid":61543,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5fd1c5f4b06f83278f0e9bc957fbce03531cedcc","tid":869403,"uid":61543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:13:40.000Z","msg":"桃園市黃姓男子與女友分手後仍常往來，去年9月間載前女友回家喝酒後親熱，事後女方告他妨害性自主。<br />\n<br />\n法院審理時，黃姓男子表示，當天是女方主動連絡到他家中喝酒聊天和過夜，二人喝了一點酒後，他摟抱、撫摸對方時，前女友說「很久沒做那件事了」，他動手脫對方衣服時，前女友沒反抗，還自已脫下內衣，2人很自然發生關係，但進行到一半時，女方突然喊停，但他停不下來，最後還是完成親熱，絕非性侵。<br />\n<br />\n黃男還出示隔天雙方的對話，包括女方「你為何沒帶套就射，不是叫你停、拿出來嗎」，男「你突然叫停，我都快出來了、hold不住，拍謝啦」，女「那懷孕怎麼辦」，男「如果要生下來我會負責，不然就...」，女「不然怎樣」，男回「love」貼圖等。<br />\n<br />\n法院傳女生訊問，她坦承主動到黃住處過夜，開始時沒拒絕對方求歡，也和黃擁抱親吻，但進行至一半時覺得有點痛，又發現對方沒戴保險套，怕懷孕才緊急喊停，但黃沒停止，算是違反她意願。<br />\n<br />\n法官查出女方是在案發後2個月才報案，且事後和黃男還有簡訊及電話連絡，卻並無責怪或怨恨語句，因此認定不是性侵，判黃男無罪。"},{"pid":"29f42ba8086faa785f99ae6d1c2f9a9c2e3e3ccb","tid":869403,"uid":187108,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:14:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a88c5671acdcfb31233375cdd0b0c5282ade528","tid":869403,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee8ad2aaa8a74b3a4792d24d0140a80b1752e8e","tid":869403,"uid":68215,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:17:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"> 女「不然怎樣」</span><br />\n唔係生就落㗎啦<br />\n老閪要個男嘅答埋啲無聊問題"},{"pid":"c40cfc1df4abe4f2024d551c2f7b6967685943f5","tid":869403,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:19:37.000Z","msg":"勞"},{"pid":"914ccfea713db85f547bc2abaa1adb831ea032e8","tid":869403,"uid":57677,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:20:04.000Z","msg":"尾嗰段先犀利"},{"pid":"76a12c66e43ea7bbd1dec2d0d91312c400708493","tid":869403,"uid":59511,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:21:06.000Z","msg":"口裡說不，最後還是被射滿滿"},{"pid":"a327c8010d976c7441841b115442def04c6197b6","tid":869403,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:32:03.000Z","msg":"love"},{"pid":"c5b43dc67433bc23e60839e11381a69fbbff7af9","tid":869403,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:33:56.000Z","msg":"好彩係台灣"},{"pid":"ac995f3da5f5dbd79a4715ce172fa83cdfc5e61e","tid":869403,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:34:59.000Z","msg":"又係台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b887f95d682d1eb61a02a822dcba2d4998aebb8d","tid":869403,"uid":22633,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"76a12c66e43ea7bbd1dec2d0d91312c400708493","tid":869403,"uid":59511,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:21:06.000Z","msg":"口裡說不，最後還是被射滿滿"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:41:29.000Z","msg":"又射滿滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ad625371603eb99f7c872adf7792df0f2dde13","tid":869403,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T12:15:28.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係新北<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}